com.wikitude.tracker

Interface CloudRecognitionService


  • public interface CloudRecognitionService
    Interface to control CloudRecognitionServices CloudRecognitionServices allow ImageTrackers to interact with the cloud recognition service

      • getClientToken

        String getClientToken()
        Returns:
        Returns the client token used when creating the CloudRecognitionService

      • getTargetCollectionId

        String getTargetCollectionId()
        Returns:
        Returns the target collection ID used when creating the CloudRecognitionService

      • isInitialized

        boolean isInitialized()
        Returns:
        Returns whether the CloudRecognitionService was successfully initialized with the chosen client token and target collection ID

      • startContinuousRecognition

        void startContinuousRecognition(double interval,
                                ContinuousCloudRecognitionServiceInterruptionListener interruptionListener,
                                CloudRecognitionServiceListener recognitionListener)
        Starts the continuous recognition mode
        Parameters:
        interval - The time span in which the CloudRecognitionService should try to recognize a target in milliseconds (suggested value: 1500-2000)
        interruptionListener - Object that will receive interruption events
        recognitionListener - Object that will receive recognition events

        Stops the continuous recognition mode
